sentences: In 1981, Daddy-O began his career as the lead member of the band Stetsasonic, which included Prince Paul, in Brooklyn, New York.
From 1994 to 1998, he was a Senior Director for MCA Records.
In 2005, Daddy-O began as Creative Director for AND1 Basketball Company, heavily involved in the Mixtape Vol.
He was given the title of Creative Director for Bitrebels.com in 2013.
2014 found Daddy-O in an executive position at PLAT4M LLC, a management consulting firm.
In 2015, Daddy-O joined the CloudSpray team as a management and marketing consultant.
In 2016, Daddy-O and his partner Lion Lindwedel (founder of True School Entertainment) formed their co-owned label, Odad Truth Records.

The first release was #EverybodyButKRS, followed in February 2016 with The Odad, the Gun, & the Children, El Dolor De Las Calles, No Tablecloths in 2018, From My Hood 2 U in 2019, and the most recent solo release of G.O.A.T. Antidote in 2020.
